en.name: Knight's Armament KAC M-LOK Barrier Grip
en.description: A lightweight foregrip designed for M-LOK handguards. Manufactured by Knight's Armament Company, the Barrier Grip provides a comfortable and secure hold on the weapon, improving control and reducing recoil during rapid fire. Its ergonomic design allows for better handling and maneuverability in various shooting positions.

en.name: Knight's Armament KAC M-LOK Finger Stop
en.description: A compact finger stop designed for M-LOK handguards. Manufactured by Knight's Armament Company, the Finger Stop provides a secure point of contact for the shooter's support hand, enhancing weapon control and stability. Its low-profile design allows for quick transitions and improved handling in various shooting scenarios.

en.name: Knight's Armament KAC M-LOK Barrier Stop
en.description: A compact barrier stop designed for M-LOK handguards. Manufactured by Knight's Armament Company, Aggressive texture for increased traction and stability on most surfaces with integral QD socket.
